How is it on top of the heads of the Sahaja
Yogis, there's all the Sahaja Yogis' heads,

00:25:43.330 --> 00:25:44.950
there is Omkara?

00:25:44.950 --> 00:25:55.900
- or Allah in Arabic language - My name also,
in Arabic.

00:25:55.900 --> 00:25:59.550
Who is doing this?

