After all you see, if you go into details,
how do you get a photograph?

00:26:39.100 --> 00:26:40.130
Through the light.

00:26:40.130 --> 00:26:44.420
The light passes straight, a straight line.

00:26:44.420 --> 00:26:50.510
But if He wants He can make the light pass
another way round.

00:26:50.510 --> 00:26:52.309
He can just transform the light into something
else.

00:26:52.309 --> 00:26:56.860
He can do whatever He likes.

00:26:56.860 --> 00:27:00.200
And that's what He does to convince you.

00:27:00.200 --> 00:27:08.990
And He said that: "Anything against Me I'll
tolerate, but nothing against the Holy Ghost."

00:27:08.990 --> 00:27:15.120
And this Holy Ghost is the Adi Shakti.

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:22.370
Without Him you cannot go to the Sahasrara.

00:27:22.370 --> 00:27:28.350
So that in the whole play He is like the [SOUNDS
