And so it is very important to pray to Shri
Ganesha every time we have Puja.

00:27:41.070 --> 00:27:48.910
We have to pray to Him and we, that's how
we are praying to Lord Jesus Christ.

00:27:48.910 --> 00:27:49.910
Every time.

00:27:49.910 --> 00:27:55.260
Without His auspiciousness, without His help,
